Package importedImplementations.TinSpinIndexes.index.qthypercube

Class QuadTreeRKD<T>

java.lang.Object
importedImplementations.TinSpinIndexes.index.qthypercube.QuadTreeRKD<T>
Type Parameters:
T - Value type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
BoxMap<T>, BoxMultimap<T>, Index
public class QuadTreeRKD<T> extends Object implements BoxMap<T>, BoxMultimap<T>
A simple MX-quadtree implementation with configurable maximum depth, maximum nodes size, and (if desired) automatic guessing of root rectangle.
Author:
ztilmann
